links.title: JetBlue Announces Update on Negotiations with TWU
links.description: JetBlue (NASDAQ: JBLU) today announced it has reached a tentative agreement with the Transport Workers Union (TWU), regarding the process toward a contract for JetBlue's inflight crewmembers. The agreement is subject to a ratification process which includes final documentation, review, and consideration by JetBlue's TWU leadership team before being distributed to inflight crewmembers for a final vote.
